OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,FA man from Wiltshire who caused an
OL,7,F"incredibly dangerous" explosion in
OL,8,Fhis own home has been jailed for more
OL,9,Fthan three years.
OL,11,FMartin Clayton, 73, poured petrol in
OL,12,Fthe living room of his rented home in
OL,13,FCaddy Lane, Mere, in the early hours
OL,14,Fof 16 December 2024 and set it alight,
OL,15,Fcausing an explosion and significant
OL,16,Fdamage.
OL,18,FThe noise woke up neighbours, who
OL,19,Fswiftly raised the alarm with the
OL,20,Femergency services.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
