FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,FClayton, now of Dudnance Lane, Pool,
OL,7,Fwas found uninjured. But the damage
OL,8,Fcaused by the explosion caused such
OL,9,Fextensive damage that the property has
OL,10,Fto be completely rebuilt, with
OL,11,Fassessment works still ongoing.
OL,13,FClayton was subsequently charged with
OL,14,Farson being reckless as to whether
OL,15,Flife was endangered.
OL,17,FHe initially pleaded not guilty, but
OL,18,Fchanged his plea just before his
OL,19,Ftrial, which was due to start in March
OL,20,F2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,FClayton was jailed for three years and
OL,7,Fone month at Salisbury Crown Court on
OL,8,FTuesday (21 April).
OL,10,FDC Martyn Powell said: "The actions of
OL,11,FMr Clayton were incredibly dangerous
OL,12,Fand put not only his own life but
OL,13,Fthose of his neighbours and the
OL,14,Fattending emergency services at risk.
OL,26,@rD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,F"There was an immediate large-scale
OL,7,Fresponse from Wiltshire Police, South
OL,8,FWestern Ambulance Service Trust and
OL,9,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,10,Fservice due to the severity of the
OL,11,Fincident - thankfully there were no
OL,12,Freported injuries, including Mr
OL,13,FClayton.
OL,15,F"I would like to praise the neighbours
OL,16,Fwho, in the early hours of the
OL,17,Fmorning, having been awoken by the
OL,18,Fexplosion, immediately contacted the
OL,19,Femergency services, helping to
OL,20,Fpreserve life and prevent further
OL,21,Fdamage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,F"My thoughts are also with the home
OL,7,Fowner, who was renting the property to
OL,8,FMr Clayton and has had to go through
OL,9,Fan ordeal of significant distress and
OL,10,Ffinancial loss due to his actions. I
OL,11,Fhope that the sentence passed today
OL,12,Fprovides some closure to them."
OL,14,FDC Powell continued: "Finally, I would
OL,15,Flike to commend the police, fire, and
OL,16,Fambulance personnel who responded to
OL,17,Fthis incident, demonstrating
OL,18,Fexceptional courage by placing
OL,19,Fthemselves in harm's way to protect
OL,20,Fnearby residents from further harm.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,F"Despite the hazardous circumstances,
OL,7,Fthey acted with compassion and
OL,8,Fprofessionalism to deal with the
OL,9,Fincident expeditiously.
OL,11,F"The response also highlighted
OL,12,Fexcellent interagency cooperation,
OL,13,Fwith effective communication and
OL,14,Fcoordination throughout a highly
OL,15,Fchallenging incident."
OL,17,FArea Manager Ant Bholah said:
OL,18,F"Incidents of this nature highlight
OL,19,Fthe importance of strong joint working
OL,20,Fbetween emergency services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
