OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776942175
OL,3,CMan who caused 'incredibly dangerous'
OL,4,Cexplosion in own home is jailed
OL,6,F"Dorset & Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService worked closely with Wiltshire
OL,8,FPolice and partner agencies to safely
OL,9,Fmanage the incident and reduce the
OL,10,Frisk to the community.
OL,12,F"Following the incident, we also
OL,13,Fcontinue to support partner
OL,14,Forganisations in the recovery and
OL,15,Finvestigation phase, recognising the
OL,16,Fimpact such events can have on
OL,17,Fresidents, property owners, and
OL,18,Fresponders alike."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@RO]
